.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-FAVICON 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
favicon \- Generate multi\-size favicons from a source image
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBfavicon\fR [\fB\-\-sizes\fR] [\fB\-\-ico\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIIMAGE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate multi\-size favicons from a source image
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-sizes\fR \fI<SIZES>\fR [default: 16,32,48,180,512]
Comma\-separated sizes (default: 16,32,48,180,512)
.TP
\fB\-\-ico\fR
Also emit a multi\-size favicon.ico
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIIMAGE\fR>

